      <t:body>
         <t:div type="edition">
            <t:div type="textpart" xml:id="Year20" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/BDLbruce90#ms_i1">
               <t:note>Beginning of the account of the 20th year of <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS5616IyasuI">ʾIyāsu I</t:persName>'s reign. A new historiographer 
               begins writing here.</t:note>
               <t:ab xml:lang="gez">ዜናሁ፡ ለ<t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS5616IyasuI#n2">
                     <t:roleName type="title">ንጉሠ፡ ነገሥት፡ </t:roleName> አድያም፡ ሰገድ፡</t:persName> 
                  ገብረ፡ ንጉሠ፡ ነገሥት፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ዘይሤለስ፡ ወይትዋሐድ። ብዙኃን፡ እለ፡
               አኃዙ፡ ይጽሐፉ፡ ወይንግሩ፡ በእንተ፡ ነገር፡ ዘንሕነ፡ ጠየቅናሁ። ባሕቱ፡ ርትዐኒ፡ ሊተ፡ ወፈቀድኩ፡ እትልዎ፡ እምጥንቱ፡ እስመ፡
               ነበርኩ፡ አነ፡ እንዘ፡ እተሉ፡ ኵሎ፡ በበመትልው፡ ወእጤይቆ፡ በጥይቅና፡ እጽሐፍ፡ ዜናሁ፡ ወመንክራቲሁ፡ 
               ለ <t:persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS5616IyasuI">
                     <t:roleName type="title">ንጉሥ፡</t:roleName>  ኢያሱ፡</t:persName> ላዕሌሁ፡ ሰላም።</t:ab>
            </t:div>
         </t:div>
      </t:body>
